{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\">The beloved classic Japanese Romaji Adventure returns in 3D!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">The remastered edition now has:</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">new music score composed in Japan</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">remastered graphics</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">new 3D battle system</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">extra features we will announce at a later date, wishlist to be notified!</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">An RPG in which you learn Japanese using romaji characters i.e. English letters.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">In a matter of hours you could be speaking Japanese. For those already learning Japanese it is a valued study addition. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">In this game you can practice and learn over 600 words along with some basic grammar.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">It is set in the 1800's and is an epic adventure that will teach you about Japanese history and the language.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1948940/extras/newweaponshows_600px.png?t=1731186441\" /><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1948940/extras/JRA3D_SS_BattleIceSword2__600px.png?t=1731186441\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>What  is it about?</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Join Harry and his crew who are among the first westerners to set foot on Japan after the prolonged period of isolation.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Set during the Meji period -- a considerably important time in Japanese history.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Face enemies and make friends along the way as you battle, quest, quiz and learn your way to victory!</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Language skills include: Intro, greetings, colors and numbers, prepositions, time, direction basic grammar.</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">The game has mini-quests and mini-games and additionally there is a battle component.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>What can you learn?</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">The ultimate goal was to make this game suitable for teaching the entire 700 words of Japanese N5. It teaches 600+ words.  It is ideal for students and/or Japan fanatics!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Story written in Japan, music composed in Japan, remastered in USA. </strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Developed by JBO Media and Angel Star Studios in partnership.</strong> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Wishlist or buy today</p>","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1948940/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1731186441","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1948940/page_bg_generated.jpg?t=1731186441","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1948940/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1731186441","capsule_imagev5":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1948940/capsule_184x69.jpg?t=1731186441","categories":[{"description":"Single-player","id":2},{"description":"Partial Controller Support","id":18}],"content_descriptors":{"ids":[],"notes":null},"detailed_description":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\">The beloved classic Japanese Romaji Adv