_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Face enemies and make friends along the way as you battle, quest, quiz and learn your way to victory!</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Language skills include: Intro, greetings, colors and numbers, prepositions, time, direction basic grammar.</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">The game has mini-quests and mini-games and additionally there is a battle component.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>What can you learn?</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">The ultimate goal was to make this game suitable for teaching the entire 700 words of Japanese N5. It teaches 600+ words.  It is ideal for students and/or Japan fanatics!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Story written in Japan, music composed in Japan, remastered in USA. </strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Developed by JBO Media and Angel Star Studios in partnership.</strong> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Wishlist or buy today</p>","developers":["JBO Media","Angel Star Studios"],"genres":[{"description":"Adventure","id":"25"},{"description":"RPG","id":"3"}],"header_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1948940/header.jpg?t=1731186441","is_free":false,"legal_notice":"Angel Star Studios, 2024","linux_requirements":{"minimum":"<strong>Minimum:</strong><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><strong>Storage:</strong> 400 MB available space</li></ul>","recommended":"<strong>Recommended:</strong><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"></ul>"},"mac_requirements":{"minimum":"<strong>Minimum:</strong><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><strong>Storage:</strong> 400 MB available space</li></ul>","recommended":"<strong>Recommended:</strong><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"></ul>"},"name":"Japanese Romaji Adventure 3D","package_groups":[],"pc_requirements":{"minimum":"<str